                            <comment id="14483712" author="sershe" created="Tue, 7 Apr 2015 18:28:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hmm... this is interesting. Do you think we should not clear HT at all and rely on GC? Is there any way to get notification of eviction from object cache?&lt;br/&gt;
Right now as I see it MapJoinOperator would clear HT after every run, so no sharing would work. I&apos;ve no idea how it even works for some cases as it is&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
